metadata.title: Disney Pixar Sully Adult Rash Guard and Swim Trunks Outfit Set Toddler to Adult
features: Disney Pixar little boys cool and stylish two piece swimsuit set for fathers and sons with short sleeve rash guard shirt and boardshort style trunks
Featuring all of your favorite animated characters from Finding Nemo, Wall-E, Bug's Life, The Incredibles, Monsters Inc., Up, Ratatouille and more in awesome sublimation print

Contrast raglan sleeves; Elastic waist for a better fit; UPF 50+ material for UVB and UVA protection and worry-free sun time; Mesh-lined shorts; 4 way stretch fabric for comfort and long-lasting fit; Functional drawstring closure
Perfect for birthday gift, Christmas holiday gift, outdoor play, swimming at the pool and beach, playing in the sun, sand and water
description: Enjoy some father/son pool time in these cool matching swim sets that show off your shared love for Pixar's animated films. This Disney Pixar set is for the little one and includes a rash guard shirt and trunks featuring a colorful geometric design of characters from the popular movies. Jump in the water with Dad and swim in style with all your favorite characters from Cars, Finding Nemo, Wall-E, Bug's Life, The Incredibles, Monsters Inc., Up, Ratatouille, and more!
